---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Personal Data Protection Notice" description="E-DOOR personal data protection and processing notice.">
  <section class="bg-background py-14 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-gutter md:px-margin">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest p-6 shadow-sm md:p-10">
        <h1 class="mb-8 font-headline text-3xl font-bold text-on-surface md:text-4xl">Personal Data Protection Notice</h1>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-sm leading-7 text-on-surface-variant">
          <p>As E-DOOR, we value the security of your personal data and process it in accordance with applicable data protection legislation, including Turkey's Personal Data Protection Law No. 6698.</p>

          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface">Personal Data We Process</h2>
            <p>Information such as your name, email address, telephone number and message content may be processed when you use our contact form.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface">Purposes of Processing</h2>
            <p>Your data is processed to respond to your requests, manage communication, prepare proposals, provide services and fulfil our legal obligations.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface">Transfer and Retention</h2>
            <p>Your personal data is not shared with third parties other than legally authorised persons and institutions. It is retained only for as long as necessary for the relevant purpose and in accordance with applicable legislation.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface">Your Rights</h2>
            <p>For information or to exercise your rights under Article 11 of Law No. 6698, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@e-door.com.tr" class="text-secondary underline hover:no-underline">info@e-door.com.tr</a>.</p>
          </div>

          <p class="border-t border-outline-variant pt-6">Address: Soğanlık Yeni Mahalle, Menderes Sokak No:4/4, Soğanlık/Kartal/İstanbul</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
